text: Kelly Carlson (born February 17, 1976) is an American actress and model. She is best known for playing Kimber Henry in Nip/Tuck. She played a motorcycle gang member in 3000 Miles to Graceland. ==Early life== Carlson was born in Minneapolis, Minnesota. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Minneapolis Category:1976 births Category:Living people
